          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蒼穹大陸，天道宗。一年一度的宗門大比今日開幕。無數弟子閉關三年，磨劍三年，只為這一刻。而林逸——蹲在比武台旁邊，用手戳牆壁。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "宗門大比正式開始。擂台之上，弟子們各展所長，劍氣縱橫。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "林逸！第一場對手是你！上場！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "哦，來了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "林逸的對手是一位煉氣期九層的師兄，靈力外放，氣勢驚人。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "這攻擊前搖也太長了吧……等等他在衝過來了！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "閃閃閃——！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "林逸慌忙後退，一腳踩進了比武台的角落——然後，穿過了牆壁。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "……我怎麼卡進來了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "等等，這個碰撞體有問題！牆壁的判定有縫隙！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "咦，對手也追過來了……他也卡住了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "哦——NPC 的尋路邏輯有缺陷，碰到邊界就會卡住不動。這不就是經典的「卡牆 Bug」嗎？"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "林逸發現，只要把對手引到比武台的邊界縫隙，他們就會被卡住，無法移動，無法出招。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "好，下一個。來來來，跟我到這裡來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "再過來一點……好，卡住了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "第二位對手被卡在了比武台邊緣，掙扎不已。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "第三個……這個精一點，不肯靠牆。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "沒關係，右邊還有個縫隙。繞一下……好，也卡住了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "這……這怎麼可能！他連手都沒抬！對手怎麼全動不了了！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "碰撞判定失效，他們現在是無敵狀態但也動不了。不過 HP 歸零判定還在……慢慢磨就行了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene3",
    "file": "04-content3.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "我看到了！師兄根本不需要出手！他只需站在那裡，對手就被「空間禁錮」了！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "空……空間禁錮？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "這一定是上古失傳的「空間禁錮之術」！以自身氣場扭曲周圍空間，將敵人封鎖在特定區域無法動彈！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "那不是傳說中渡劫期以上才能施展的禁術嗎……？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老你看！師兄連續用了好幾次，每次位置都不同！說明他能精確控制空間扭曲的座標！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "（偷偷拿出筆記本）「卡……卡模型……」不對，這名字太俗了……「空間禁錮……以氣場扭曲空間……需找到特定的節點……」"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "什麼節點？我就是看哪裡有縫隙而已。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "師兄說的「縫隙」就是空間的裂縫！他能直接看到空間結構的弱點！"
      }
    ]
  },
